column5: Hi There,  What will be a good store with cheap shipping rates and if possible from Canada? I don't want o pay imports. Thank you for any info.  Happy holidays.
Our boss TJ has a store on the board.
eTackle.ca is in durham region so shipping to you wouldn't be to bad.  vance
What are you looking for? That would narrow it down abit.
eTackle.ca is in durham region so shipping to you wouldn't be to bad.  vance  I haven't been able to open etackle.ca for while Anybody else finding this to be the case?

I haven't been able to open etackle.ca for while Anybody else finding this to be the case?  I think he is having health or family issues and is not actively selling at this point.  I still order a lot of stuff for Lebarons.

I think he is having health or family issues and is not actively selling at this point.  I still order a lot of stuff for Lebarons. Last time I talked to him that seemed to be the case, hope all is well!
My vote is for The fishin hole. Great prices and cheap shipping

Last I heard, Etackle scammed a bunch of people. Glad I didnt order from them. I know phil is alive and well, and has a new job, but not sure whats up with the tackle scamming....i mean business.  S. I heard it was just slow shipping

It just depends on what you are looking for, so what do you need?  You can order directly from alot of the dealers, last time I ordered online I went through the approved lists on the Canadian Made and North American Made facebook pages.  Most of the companies will ship and if you buy directly they sometimes throw in a bonus.  Here is a link to the "Canadian Made" https://www.facebook.com/CanadianMadeOutdoorsGear  I thought their link to the Seal skin boots was interesting.... until I saw the price! http://www.furcanada.com/seal-skin.html
You have a number of independent makers of custom tackle right here on OFC. Custom makers of rods, flies, streamers, harnesses, spinners, musky baits,..... It all depends on what you are looking for.
What if you need a whole bunch of Downrigging Salmon / Trout stuff ?  Torpedo Divers Dipsys Jets Planers  Etc etc

Check out Land Big Fish. com Great selection I didnt pay any additional / hidden costs for duty Shipped in a couple of days. I also had the chance to stop in the store last winter when in Ohio. Great guys , very helpfull and knowledgable I have ordered from them numerous times. http://www.landbigfish.com/
Right now the fishin hole has free shipping over $50. Not bad.
Right now the fishin hole has free shipping over $50. Not bad. I can think of a few guys on here who are cheaper than that
how about www.wannabefisherman.com/shop for something a bit different?
